Preferred Term ( MedDRA  Version: 18.0 ReC
The physician did not provide the causal relationship of progressive multifocal leukoencephalopathy with rituximab.
The physician assessed the progressive multifocal leukoencephalopathy as medically significant.
No further information was provided.